Class GameResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • pente.GameResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<GameResult>

    public class GameResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<GameResult>
    A GameResult stores the win/loss totals of an individual player. To keep track of the tournament rankings, a List of GameResults is kept and sorted in order from highest total wins to lowest total wins.
    Author:
    eric_ferrante
